colnames(contrast_design) <- levels(condition_factor)

                             SW_vs_HS_noN_HO=SW_noN_HO-HS_noN_HO,

DE_table <- summary(decideTests(contrast_fit,adjust.method="fdr",p.value = 0.05,lfc = 1))
DE_table <- as.data.frame(DE_table)


maketable<-function(contrast_name){
  x<-topTable(contrast_fit, adjust="BH",coef=contrast_name, p.value=1, number=Inf ,resort.by="P")
  colnames(x)<-paste(contrast_name,colnames(x),sep=".")
  x$geneid<-row.names(x)
  rownames(x)<-NULL
  return(x)
}
